      "date": "2012-01-17 12:03:57.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.7/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/8fe30166-4101-11e1-972d-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
